          h2 Contact 
            span.thin Us
          ul.list-unstyled
            li.icon-phone (315) 523-0939
            li.icon-map Serving Auburn, Skaneateles,
            li Elbridge, Camillus, Weedsport, Port Byron, Cayuga, Union Springs, Seneca Falls, Waterloo, Geneva and surrounding areas.
